author: hoju
msg: Add target="1.2" and source="1.3" attributes to all usages of <javac> to make sure that classes are compatible with JDK1.2+ no matter what JDK under which the compilation is done.  This mirrors what was done to the 1.2 branch while taking into account usage of JDK1.2 features where the 1.2 branch needs to stay compatible with JDk1.1.
